<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .header { color: #10b981; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; }
        .button { background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">You're verified!</div>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Great news! Our team has reviewed your profile and farm details. Your application to join Bleefy as a verified partner has been <strong>approved</strong>.</p>
        <p>You can now log in to your dashboard to start listing your produce and managing your sales.</p>
        
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Bleefy Agri-Marketplace. This is an automated message.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>